So we called an ambulance.

787
01:40:39,451 --> 01:40:40,880
Are you there?

788
01:40:52,859 --> 01:40:54,997
What happened, Dad?

789
01:42:16,928 --> 01:42:18,865
What's going on?

790
01:42:29,914 --> 01:42:31,544
What happened?

791
01:42:32,378 --> 01:42:34,105
Are you OK?

792
01:42:49,919 --> 01:42:50,840
Well...

793
01:42:53,343 --> 01:42:54,801
I will...

794
01:42:56,191 --> 01:42:58,742
I'll answer your proposal.

795
01:43:01,025 --> 01:43:01,965
What?

796
01:43:05,465 --> 01:43:09,042
Your proposal...

797
01:43:10,682 --> 01:43:12,543
I accept.

798
01:43:17,376 --> 01:43:18,901
Proposal?

799
01:43:27,418 --> 01:43:29,556
It's like a dream.

800
01:43:32,194 --> 01:43:34,706
I'm so happy.

801
01:43:39,454 --> 01:43:41,726
I applied for the audition.

802
01:43:43,577 --> 01:43:45,591
I was the...

803
01:43:48,545 --> 01:43:50,195
...luckiest one.

804
01:43:52,669 --> 01:43:56,409
Because I didn't become
the heroine of the movie.

805
01:43:57,368 --> 01:43:59,987
But I became the real heroine.

806
01:44:25,497 --> 01:44:26,964
Deeper, deeper...

807
01:44:28,537 --> 01:44:30,714
What's wrong, Dad?

808
01:44:35,835 --> 01:44:37,082
Who the hell are you?

809
01:44:42,587 --> 01:44:44,659
What the hell do you want?

810
01:44:54,009 --> 01:44:54,940
What's going on?

811
01:45:48,569 --> 01:45:49,749
Dad!

812
01:45:51,130 --> 01:45:53,038
Are you alright, Dad?

813
01:45:54,016 --> 01:45:55,091
Dad!

814
01:45:57,853 --> 01:45:59,704
Call the police...

815
01:45:59,905 --> 01:46:01,238
Police...

816
01:46:08,958 --> 01:46:13,082
Is this the police? This is the Aoyama
residence, Okusawa.

817
01:46:13,245 --> 01:46:15,221
Please send an ambulance.

818
01:46:16,698 --> 01:46:18,971
My father's been seriously injured.
And one woman too.

819
01:46:19,258 --> 01:46:21,464
I don't know the details.

820
01:46:23,162 --> 01:46:27,803
His left leg has been chopped off
and is bleeding badly.

821
01:46:31,707 --> 01:46:35,898
The address is Okusawa 6-20-4.

822
01:46:37,375 --> 01:46:39,791
I thought you were very busy.

823
01:46:41,853 --> 01:46:44,471
I don't know your job so well.

824
01:46:45,881 --> 01:46:50,638
I might sound heavy.

825
01:46:52,384 --> 01:46:56,239
But I've been waiting for
your call for a long time.

826
01:47:10,270 --> 01:47:14,969
I never expected that
we would meet again.

827
01:47:15,228 --> 01:47:18,364
Sorry to have been childish.

828
01:47:20,608 --> 01:47:24,406
It's a hassle living alone.

829
01:47:25,691 --> 01:47:29,172
I didn't have anybody to talk with.

830
01:47:31,743 --> 01:47:34,361
You are the first one to support me...

831
01:47:35,003 --> 01:47:37,372
Warmly wrapping me...

832
01:47:37,593 --> 01:47:40,662
Trying to understand me...

833
01:47:41,151 --> 01:47:44,862
It's hard to forget about.

834
01:47:50,521 --> 01:47:52,794
But someday you'll feel...

835
01:47:53,340 --> 01:47:57,685
...that life is wonderful.

836
01:47:59,104 --> 01:48:02,326
That's life, isn't it?

